  <Technique
    id={"t2"}
    title={"T2. Auto-compact before-turn + reactive on overflow"}
    tid={"A.2"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/engine/query.py</code> · <strong>Lines:</strong> 519–562 · <strong>Service:</strong> <code>services/compact/</code> · <strong>Hằng:</strong> <code>AUTOCOMPACT_BUFFER_TOKENS = 13_000</code>"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="com"># 1. Before-turn
      auto-compact</span> <span class="kw">async for</span> event, usage <span
      class="kw">in</span> _stream_compaction(trigger=<span
      class="str">"auto"</span>): <span class="kw">yield</span> event, usage
      messages, was_compacted = last_compaction_result <span class="com"># 2.
      Reactive compact khi provider trả prompt-too-long</span> <span
      class="kw">except</span> Exception <span class="kw">as</span> exc:
      error_msg = str(exc) <span class="kw">if not</span>
      reactive_compact_attempted <span class="kw">and</span>
      _is_prompt_too_long_error(exc): reactive_compact_attempted = <span
      class="kw">True</span> <span class="kw">yield</span>
      StatusEvent(message=REACTIVE_COMPACT_STATUS_MESSAGE), <span
      class="kw">None</span> <span class="kw">async for</span> event, usage
      <span class="kw">in</span> _stream_compaction(trigger=<span
      class="str">"reactive"</span>, force=<span class="kw">True</span>): <span
      class="kw">yield</span> event, usage messages, was_compacted =
      last_compaction_result <span class="kw">if</span> was_compacted: <span
      class="kw">continue</span> <span class="com"># retry turn với messages đã
      compact</span> <span class="com"># 3. services/compact/microcompact.py —
      cheap, fast first pass</span> <span class="com"># Drop stale
      ToolResultBlock content (keep tool_use structure)</span> <span
      class="com"># 4. services/compact/summary.py — LLM summarize khi
      microcompact không đủ</span> <span class="com"># 5.
      services/compact/ptl_retry.py — truncate_head_for_ptl_retry()</span> <span
      class="com"># last-chance cắt head khi reactive vẫn
      overflow</span></code></pre> <div class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan
      trọng:</strong> Ba tầng compaction phòng vệ: (1) <em>proactive</em> —
      trước mỗi turn ước lượng token, nếu gần giới hạn chạy microcompact xóa
      tool_result cũ; (2) <em>reactive</em> — khi API trả 400 "prompt too long",
      retry với LLM summary; (3) <em>last-resort</em> — nếu vẫn overflow,
      truncate head messages. Điều này giúp session dài (hàng trăm turn) không
      bị die. Buffer 13k tokens là "đệm" cho response + tool output của turn
      kế.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4> <pre><code><span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">CompactionOrchestrator</span>:
      <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">maybe_compact</span>(self, messages, trigger=<span
      class="str">"auto"</span>): estimate =
      self.token_counter.estimate(messages) <span class="kw">if</span> estimate
      &lt; self.threshold: <span class="kw">return</span> messages, <span
      class="kw">False</span> <span class="com"># Phase 1: cheap — drop old
      ToolResultBlock content only</span> pruned = self.microcompact(messages)
      <span class="kw">if</span> self.token_counter.estimate(pruned) &lt;
      self.threshold: <span class="kw">return</span> pruned, <span
      class="kw">True</span> <span class="com"># Phase 2: expensive — LLM
      summarize</span> summary = <span class="kw">await</span>
      self.llm_summarize(pruned) <span class="kw">return</span> [system_prompt,
      summary] + pruned[-<span class="num">5</span>:], <span
      class="kw">True</span> <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">run_turn</span>(self, messages): messages, _ = <span
      class="kw">await</span> self.maybe_compact(messages) <span
      class="kw">try</span>: <span class="kw">return await</span>
      llm.call(messages) <span class="kw">except</span> PromptTooLongError:
      messages, _ = <span class="kw">await</span> self.maybe_compact(messages,
      trigger=<span class="str">"reactive"</span>) <span class="kw">return
      await</span> llm.call(messages) <span class="com"># one
      retry</span></code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Ba-tầng graceful — rẻ trước, đắt sau",
