  <Technique
    id={"t3"}
    title={"T3. Streaming events union + CompactProgressEvent 9-phase"}
    tid={"A.3"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/engine/stream_events.py</code> · <strong>Lines:</strong> toàn bộ file"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">from dataclasses
      import</span> dataclass <span class="kw">from typing import</span>
      Literal, Union <span class="com"># 7 event types yielded from
      run_query()</span> <span class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">AssistantTextDelta</span>:
      text: str <span class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">AssistantTurnComplete</span>:
      message: ConversationMessage; usage: UsageSnapshot <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">ToolExecutionStarted</span>: tool_name: str;
      tool_input: dict <span class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">ToolExecutionCompleted</span>:
      tool_name: str; output: object; is_error: bool <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">StatusEvent</span>: message: str <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">ErrorEvent</span>: message: str <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">CompactProgressEvent</span>: phase: Literal[ <span
      class="str">"hooks_start"</span>, <span
      class="str">"context_collapse_start"</span>, <span
      class="str">"context_collapse_end"</span>, <span
      class="str">"session_memory_start"</span>, <span
      class="str">"session_memory_end"</span>, <span
      class="str">"compact_start"</span>, <span
      class="str">"compact_retry"</span>, <span
      class="str">"compact_end"</span>, <span
      class="str">"compact_failed"</span>, ] message: str StreamEvent = Union[
      AssistantTextDelta, AssistantTurnComplete, ToolExecutionStarted,
      ToolExecutionCompleted, StatusEvent, ErrorEvent, CompactProgressEvent,
      ]</code></pre> <div class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan trọng:</strong> Thay
      vì union mơ hồ <code>dict[str, Any]</code>, OpenHarness dùng <em>tagged
      union</em> với <code>@dataclass(frozen=True)</code>. UI bên Rich/Textual
      pattern-match bằng <code>isinstance()</code> cho từng event type — mypy
      strict đảm bảo không bỏ sót case. Event đặc biệt nhất là
      <code>CompactProgressEvent</code> với 9 phase: UI hiện progress bar chi
      tiết (đang collapse context → đang save memory → đang summarize →
      done/fail) thay vì chỉ "compacting...". Mức độ observability này trong bản
      port Python rất hiếm.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4>
      <pre><code><span class="kw">from typing import</span> Union, Literal <span
      class="kw">from dataclasses import</span> dataclass <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">TextDelta</span>: text: str <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">ToolStart</span>: tool: str; input: dict <span
      class="fn">@dataclass(frozen=True)</span> <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">ToolEnd</span>: tool: str; output: str; error: bool
      Event = Union[TextDelta, ToolStart, ToolEnd] <span class="kw">async
      def</span> <span class="fn">render_events</span>(gen): <span
      class="kw">async for</span> ev <span class="kw">in</span> gen: match ev:
      <span class="kw">case</span> TextDelta(text): console.print(text,
      end=<span class="str">""</span>) <span class="kw">case</span>
      ToolStart(tool, _): ui.mark_tool(tool, <span class="str">"running"</span>)
      <span class="kw">case</span> ToolEnd(tool, _, error): ui.mark_tool(tool,
      <span class="str">"error"</span> <span class="kw">if</span> error <span
      class="kw">else</span> <span class="str">"done"</span>)</code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Type-safe: mypy strict bắt bỏ sót case",
        "UI logic tách rời khỏi engine",
        "CompactProgressEvent 9-phase → UX chi tiết lúc compact",
        "Dễ serialize sang JSON cho remote UI",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Thêm event type cần cập nhật nhiều chỗ (engine + UI + tests)",
        'Frozen dataclass immutable → không "accumulate" được (phải tạo object mới mỗi delta)',
        "Không có ID liên kết parent-child event (tool_start ↔ tool_end phải match bằng tool_name)",
      ]}
    />
    <RefList
      items={[
        '<a href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/dataclasses.html">Python docs — dataclasses (frozen)</a>',
        '<a href="https://docs.pydantic.dev/latest/">Pydantic — discriminated unions</a>',
        '<a href="https://opentelemetry.io/blog/2025/ai-agent-observability/">OpenTelemetry — AI Agent Observability (2025)</a>',
      ]}
    />
  </Technique>
  <Technique
    id={"t4"}
    title={"T4. Pre/Post tool hook interception"}
    tid={"A.4"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/engine/query.py</code> · <strong>Hàm:</strong> <code>_execute_tool_call()</code> · <strong>Lines:</strong> 654–720"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">async def</span>
      <span class="fn">_execute_tool_call</span>( context: QueryContext,
      tool_name: str, tool_use_id: str, tool_input: dict[str, object], ) -&gt;
      ToolResultBlock: <span class="com"># ---- PRE_TOOL_USE hook ----</span>
      <span class="kw">if</span> context.hook_executor <span class="kw">is not
      None</span>: pre_hooks = <span class="kw">await</span>
      context.hook_executor.execute( HookEvent.PRE_TOOL_USE, {<span
      class="str">"tool_name"</span>: tool_name, <span
      class="str">"tool_input"</span>: tool_input, <span
      class="str">"event"</span>: HookEvent.PRE_TOOL_USE.value}, ) <span
      class="kw">if</span> pre_hooks.blocked: <span class="kw">return</span>
      ToolResultBlock( tool_use_id=tool_use_id, content=pre_hooks.reason <span
      class="kw">or</span> <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"pre_tool_use hook blocked {tool_name}"</span>, is_error=<span
      class="kw">True</span>, ) <span class="com"># ---- Actual tool execution
      ----</span> result = <span class="kw">await</span>
      context.tool_registry.execute(tool_name, tool_input, ...) <span
      class="com"># ---- POST_TOOL_USE hook (observation only, cannot block)
      ----</span> <span class="kw">if</span> context.hook_executor <span
      class="kw">is not None</span>: <span class="kw">await</span>
      context.hook_executor.execute( HookEvent.POST_TOOL_USE, {<span
      class="str">"tool_name"</span>: tool_name, <span
      class="str">"tool_input"</span>: tool_input, <span
      class="str">"tool_result"</span>: result.content, <span
      class="str">"is_error"</span>: result.is_error}, ) <span
      class="kw">return</span> result</code></pre> <div class="why"><strong>Tại
      sao quan trọng:</strong> Hook cho phép user/plugin inject policy
      <em>ngoài</em> permission system — ví dụ: chặn <code>git push</code> sau
      6pm, log bash vào SIEM, validate Edit pattern. PRE hook có thể
      <em>blocked=True</em> → short-circuit thành ToolResultBlock error (LLM
      thấy như tool fail bình thường, tự điều chỉnh). POST hook chỉ observe —
      không thể undo execution đã xong. Thiết kế này giống Claude Code hooks
      (tham chiếu <code>code.claude.com/docs/en/hooks</code>).</div> <h4>Code
      example (generic)</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">HookExecutor</span>: <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">execute</span>(self, event: HookEvent, payload: dict) -&gt;
      HookResult: blocked = <span class="kw">False</span>; reason = <span
      class="kw">None</span> <span class="kw">for</span> hook <span
      class="kw">in</span> self.hooks.get(event, []): res = <span
      class="kw">await</span> hook.run(payload) <span class="kw">if</span>
      res.blocked: blocked = <span class="kw">True</span>; reason = res.reason;
      <span class="kw">break</span> <span class="kw">return</span>
      HookResult(blocked=blocked, reason=reason) <span class="com"># Usage
      inside tool execution</span> <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">run_tool</span>(name, args): pre = <span
      class="kw">await</span> hooks.execute(HookEvent.PRE_TOOL_USE, {<span
      class="str">"tool_name"</span>: name, <span class="str">"args"</span>:
      args}) <span class="kw">if</span> pre.blocked: <span
      class="kw">return</span> {<span class="str">"error"</span>: pre.reason
      <span class="kw">or</span> <span class="str">"blocked by hook"</span>}
      result = <span class="kw">await</span> tool.execute(args) <span
      class="kw">await</span> hooks.execute(HookEvent.POST_TOOL_USE, {<span
      class="str">"tool_name"</span>: name, <span class="str">"result"</span>:
      result}) <span class="kw">return</span> result</code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Policy tách khỏi permission system — hai layer bảo vệ",
        "PRE có thể block; POST có thể audit/log",
        "Hot-reload hooks qua <code>HookReloader</code> watch mtime",
        "Shell/Prompt/HTTP/Agent types — đa dạng",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Hook chạy sync trong hot path → latency mỗi tool",
        "Prompt hook gọi LLM → cost + race với main loop",
        'Không có "retry with modified args" — chỉ block or pass',
        "Hook mis-config có thể làm agent stuck mà khó debug",
      ]}
    />
    <RefList
      items={[
        '<a href="https://code.claude.com/docs/en/hooks">Claude Code — Hooks documentation</a>',
        '<a href="https://dev.to/klement_gunndu/lock-down-claude-code-with-5-permission-patterns-4gcn">DEV — 5 Permission Patterns in Claude Code</a>',
        '<a href="https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/claude-code-auto-mode">Anthropic — Claude Code auto mode</a>',
      ]}
    />
  </Technique>
  <Technique
    id={"t5"}
